<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 01:21:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿尔茨海默病的突破：科学家发现关键蛋白质可以预防大脑中的有毒蛋白质团块</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/alzheimers-breakthrough-scientists-discover-key-protein-may-prevent-toxic-protein-clumps-in-the-brain</link><description>新的研究表明，微管蛋白可能有助于预防与阿尔茨海默病和帕金森病相关的有毒蛋白质团块。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/alzheimers-breakthrough-scientists-discover-key-protein-may-prevent-toxic-protein-clumps-in-the-brain.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 01:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/alzheimers-breakthrough-scientists-discover-key-protein-may-prevent-toxic-protein-clumps-in-the-brain</guid></item><item><title>科学家在活体小鼠大脑中培育电子器件</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-grow-electronics-inside-the-brains-of-living-mice</link><description>然而，大多数植入物需要进行大量手术，并且有损坏大脑脆弱组织的风险。新技术将通过直接在目标上构建电极来避免这些缺点。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-grow-electronics-inside-the-brains-of-living-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 01:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-grow-electronics-inside-the-brains-of-living-mice</guid></item><item><title>一位企业家正在将冷战时期的核发射井改造成地下数据中心。看看里面</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/an-entrepreneur-is-transforming-a-cold-war-era-nuclear-silo-into-an-underground-data-center-look-inside</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/an-entrepreneur-is-transforming-a-cold-war-era-nuclear-silo-into-an-underground-data-center-look-inside</guid></item><item><title>切片和切丁</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/slice-and-dice</link><description>麻省理工学院的研究人员对 SNIPE 进行了描述，它代表表面相关核酸酶抑制噬菌体进入，它通过在病毒进入细菌时切断入侵的病毒 DNA，直接保护细菌免受噬菌体（感染它们的病毒）的侵害。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/slice-and-dice2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/slice-and-dice</guid></item><item><title>大型科技教学机器是否具有意识？ Google Mind 聘请哲学家的举动引起了人们的注意</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/is-big-tech-teaching-machines-to-be-conscious-google-minds-move-to-hire-a-philosopher-raises-eyebrows</link><description>在谷歌 DeepMind 悄悄聘请了一位内部哲学家来研究机器意识的潜力之后，构建更智能的人工智能的竞赛发生了意想不到的哲学转变…… &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/is-big-tech-teaching-machines-to-be-conscious-google-minds-move-to-hire-a-philosopher-raises-eyebrows2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/is-big-tech-teaching-machines-to-be-conscious-google-minds-move-to-hire-a-philosopher-raises-eyebrows</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的 xAI 对科罗拉多州的人工智能反歧视法提起诉讼，声称这对 Grok 的言论自由构成威胁</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/elon-musks-xai-sues-over-colorados-ai-antidiscrimination-law-claiming-its-a-threat-to-groks-free-speech</link><description>参议院第 205 号法案于 2024 年通过，是美国监管“高风险”人工智能系统并保护消费者免受“算法歧视”的首次尝试之一，即科罗拉多州法律规定的对受保护阶层的差别待遇或影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/elon-musks-xai-sues-over-colorados-ai-antidiscrimination-law-claiming-its-a-threat-to-groks-free-speech.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/elon-musks-xai-sues-over-colorados-ai-antidiscrimination-law-claiming-its-a-threat-to-groks-free-speech</guid></item><item><title>P53：从了解其结构到治疗靶向的进展——信号转导和靶向治疗</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/p53-from-understanding-its-structure-to-advances-in-therapeutic-targeting-signal-transduction-and-targeted-therapy</link><description>王文、刘X、刘H. &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/p53-from-understanding-its-structure-to-advances-in-therapeutic-targeting-signal-transduction-and-targeted-therapy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 23:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/p53-from-understanding-its-structure-to-advances-in-therapeutic-targeting-signal-transduction-and-targeted-therapy</guid></item><item><title>物理学家刚刚目睹了黑暗中的针刺移动速度超过光速，而没有违反相对论</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/physicists-just-witnessed-pinpricks-of-darkness-moving-faster-than-the-speed-of-light-without-breaking-the-laws-of-relativity</link><description>研究人员首次测量了移动速度超过光速的光波和声波组合的奇点。这些发现对流体动力学、光学和许多其他领域都有影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-just-witnessed-pinpricks-of-darkness-moving-faster-than-the-speed-of-light-without-breaking-the-laws-of-relativity.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 23:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/physicists-just-witnessed-pinpricks-of-darkness-moving-faster-than-the-speed-of-light-without-breaking-the-laws-of-relativity</guid></item><item><title>地球太空 2026</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/earthspace-2026</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 23:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/earthspace-2026</guid></item><item><title>伤害感受神经元保护癌细胞免受氧化应激</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nociceptive-neurons-protect-cancer-cells-against-oxidative-stress</link><description>癌细胞如何利用肿瘤微环境来减轻氧化应激尚不清楚。张等人。发现伤害性神经元通过分泌 EREG 保护 HNSCC 免受氧化应激诱导的细胞死亡。针对伤害性神经元可提高化疗（包括顺铂）的治疗效果。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nociceptive-neurons-protect-cancer-cells-against-oxidative-stress.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 23:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nociceptive-neurons-protect-cancer-cells-against-oxidative-stress</guid></item></channel></rss>